                     <note>
                        <p>An Urdu translation of Saʿdī's Gulistān.</p>
                        <p>No 96 in J.F. Blumhardt, Catalogue of the Hindi, Panjabi and Hindustani manuscripts in the Library of the British Museum. London, 1899</p>
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
